25 September 2015Minister of Home Affairs, Malusi Gigaba, in his capacity as the Chairperson of the Governance and Administration (G&amp;A) Cluster, will lead a media briefing to give an update on progress and achievements made in the implementation of the clusters programme of action. Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Sunday, 27 September 2015 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria NB: There will be a video link to the Imbizo Media Centre at Parliament, Cape Town Kindly confirm attendance by email or sms to: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) E-mail: Ireen@gcis.gov.za Cell: 082 440 5676 Andile Duka (Cape Town) E-mail: Andiled@gcis.gov.za Cell: 071 154 5619Follow the briefing on Twitter by using the hashtag #GAbriefing Enquiries: Legadima Leso on 083 378 9495Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)